Package api

Class DWGraph_DS

java.lang.Object
api.DWGraph_DS
All Implemented Interfaces:
directed_weighted_graph
public class DWGraph_DS
extends java.lang.Object
implements directed_weighted_graph
this class is presenting a directional weighted (positive) graph. . the graph is contains nodes who are very similar to dots inside regular graph in this class we can add and delete nodes , connect between them or disconnect, who connect to who is important. get know the edge between two nodes if there is any and get the information of any node inside the graph. all the nodes must have a unique key. in addition - the graph remember the number of nodes, edges and how many changes was make.
Author:
liadn7, avielc11
